Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下了去干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去与Master汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯背叛组织逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被那家伙抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要与Master汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能汇合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就协助他的逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中搅局的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能瓦解组织的追击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  任务还是进行中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后也应该和我一起执行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡中的赛斯现在也在Phantom的保护之下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯身上缠绕着人们对Phantom的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  组织也不会鲁莽行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里被抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对赛斯也只有负面影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了呢  Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和昨天的你判若二人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你已经不是Zwei了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你现在是吾妻玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有真正的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…我却
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的只是数字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归宿只有Master的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Master给我的这个叫Ein的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不是的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没想过我会消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然很乱来  但不是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到被劫走的运输车了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像空有躯壳而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯是你养的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就由你这个狗主人了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  很吵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  好像叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然曲名忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在大街上经常听到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本  大家都听这样的歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐上的喜好会因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在洛杉矶和日本都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我听听日本的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经想起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为吾妻玲二生活时的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物按照原定计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡路线也好  搬入路线也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头到尾都在你的手掌心里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等安定下来再联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也合作愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不能信任的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能整个梧桐组就被出卖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了我们而利用那个女人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还怕什么啊  志贺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要登上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾妻玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是不知道我在这半年间都做了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已经回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你有你的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为吾妻玲二  存在于这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一样吗  也好好地在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有我没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有能证明自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有这个真的这么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这就是你作为你自己的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是些纸屑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我作为我自己的只有过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  这些你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是跟我说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺眼般的明亮和强烈的风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你家乡的记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很暧昧的记忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能保证它就是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这就是你的记忆  你也有自己的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Ein这样的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想对你见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持这个意志  这就是证明我自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以靠印章和这些纸屑来证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出示驾驶执照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪儿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探望朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃列斯·杨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来更年轻一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也常常被人家这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气色很差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为长途旅行  有点晕车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熟练了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  刚才的演技？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  不都是你教的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边移动  一边像这样让你休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤好了之后  就到远方去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧  这是自己的意志决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点吃的来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein  Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明直到昨天为止都没感觉到一丝恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  手指无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二  你来开枪  让我解脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自说自话了吧  到底怎么了  Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是比我更坚强的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是为了Master  别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Master的指示  就算要背叛组织都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  现在的我到底是为了什么而活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被组织追杀  只能一味逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连扳机都扣不下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天要是能死在那的话  至少还能作为Ein死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样说  我们一直是为了死而战斗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们是为了活下去而战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你死在这种鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你活下去  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正被Inferno追杀  要是追兵追到这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会把枪指向我还是组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说  向组织开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以我的意志扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么你为了活下去能做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我也像你一样活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经谁也不是  一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去的理由和使命都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不叫你Ein了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein也只是个数字  不是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要新的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是Phantom  也不是数字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为你而活的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦  就叫爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始我就称呼你爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管什么理由  这是我决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是杀手也不是人偶  你作为你活下去的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦…爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦  去寻找吧  寻找你失去的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找回真正的名字  就能找到一大堆活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样会伤害到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也会想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在可能很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是走吧  和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上的那个  要是就这样归依赛斯的话  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把现金和车弄来  一小时后回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不剧烈运动就没有大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦  玲二给我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以这个名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊  Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛这点小事  用精神力克服它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太执着了  Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚的蜜月过得开心不？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被赛斯摆布了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟赛斯没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我会慢慢问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有消息来  说尾行Phantom的部下被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom回到赛斯手下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多也该给我坦白了吧  赛斯去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  他好像什么都不知道的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我吧  你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就承认你的顽固吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克风已经关了  说什么都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出Ein然后两人逃走  这就是你的选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊  你已经帮助了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是被怀疑的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提什么回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你还有可以减刑的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有证明自己的清白  夺回Ein的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话该明白吧  这东西的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛斯由我来杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告  终幕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱伦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会让你笑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回你普通的笑容


